column5: Hey everyone not sure if youll remember me i was on a lot in the summer and usual am,i dont know why i always drift away from the forum in the winter, probably because i dont fish and am caught up in lifes obsticals anyways its nice to be back!
welcome back, you know you still can fish in the winter!
Welcome back -Little Angler..... I was wondering what happen to you... last time you posted was this summer about the tournament between you and Mike The Bass Fisher
I post more in the winter...mostly because I dont enjoy the cold.  welcome back
welcome back. the fall is a very busy time for me so i go weeks without hitting OFC but then jan comes and im here everyday until spring lol  cheers!
